snippet.title: Garbageboi+ (Trailer)
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD: https://noxlof.itch.io/garbageboiplus

That's right! The new and improved Garbageboi is here!

As a Garbageboi, you clean the streets while avoiding insane traffic and the deadly stares from the people living there.

Game by: Lucas Gullbo (@Noxlof)
Music by: Anes Sabanovic (@anessabanovic_)
